
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-dane-smtp-with-dane-19.txt'>
    <title>"SMTP security via opportunistic DANE TLS", Viktor Dukhovni, Wesley Hardaker</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-dane-smtp-with-dane-19.txt</link>
    <description>This memo describes a downgrade-resistant protocol for SMTP transport security between Mail Transfer Agents (MTAs) based on the DNS-Based Authentication of Named Entities (DANE) TLSA DNS record.  Adoption of this protocol enables an incremental transition of the Internet email backbone to one using encrypted and authenticated Transport Layer Security (TLS).</description>
    <dc:date>2015-05-29T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
